Demonstratives occur in the ko- , so- , and a- series . The ko- ( proximal ) series refers to things closer to the speaker than the hearer , the so- ( mesial ) series for things closer to the 
hearer , and the a- ( distal ) series for things distant to both the speaker and the hearer . With do- , demonstratives turn into the corresponding question form . Demonstratives can also 
